sql:
SELECT MAX(player_count) AS max_players_in_position
FROM (
  SELECT COUNT(*) AS player_count
  FROM players
  GROUP BY position
);

external_knowledge:
- This question assumes a level of familiarity with sports terminology; 
Player seasons are ordered chronologically; 
Cumulative wins and losses refer to the aggregate wins and losses a player has achieved up to a certain point in their career.
